data.description: Best panoramic view in Plainfield - pond, wetlands and walking trails all viewable from balcony, deck, master bedroom & yard. Built with tons of extra features including expanded 3 car garage, morning room and finished walkout basement with media room. There's also a 1st floor office, 2nd floor loft, huge 23x16 master bedroom with luxury bath and 2nd bedroom with private bath. This great home also features a 2nd floor laundry, newer zoned furnace/ac, water filtration system, Andersen windows & much more. Located in Springbank, this home has it all including access to Springbank Aquatic Center. Save big on this home with a special financing opportunity, assumable mortgage at 5.5% - contact agent for details!
